text: Kwajalein Jr./Sr. High School is a secondary school in Kwajalein, Marshall Islands. It is a part of Kwajalein Range Services. The school serves families in the US military and civilians working for the US government. ==References== ==External links== * Kwajalein Junior/Senior High School * Kwajalein Junior/Senior High School old site at Tripod.com Category:Schools in the Marshall Islands Category:Kwajalein Atoll Category:High schools
